    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "About This Example Set",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 12,
        "w": 10,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 4
      },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Log Search\n\nA realistic log viewer demonstrating how DataTable handles timestamped, level-tagged log data.\n\n### Features demonstrated\n\n- \ud83d\udcc5 **Timestamp formatting** \u2014 DATE style formats raw timestamps\n- \ud83c\udfa8 **Level coloring** \u2014 ERROR=red, WARN=orange, INFO=blue, DEBUG=gray\n- \ud83d\udd22 **Value mappings** \u2014 0/1/2/3 \u2192 DEBUG/INFO/WARN/ERROR\n- \ud83d\udd0d **Search with highlighting** \u2014 search matches are highlighted in yellow\n- \ud83d\udd3d **Column filters** \u2014 filter dropdowns on each column\n- \ud83d\udccf **Wide message column** \u2014 50% width hint\n\n[Open Log Search \u2192](/d/dt-logs)",
        "code": {
          "language": "plaintext",
          "showLineNumbers": false,
          "showMiniMap": false
        }
      },
      "targets": []
    },
